channel.title: Cat help
channel.description:
Seriously I've gone through like 11 kittens on RS. And I just end up forgetting to feed them due to skilling, but guys what are some ways I could blow hours of just walking around.
Such as questing for pures, I've done all the RFD for mith (need a cat for addy), and I've done DT, MM, and Underground Pass

item.title: Cat help
item.dc:creator: @Mawnster Mawnster
item.description:
@Mawnster wrote:

A window pops up in your chat box, that says something along the lines of… “I think it’s hungry”, that, is when you run to a bank, and give it something to eat. Also, stroke your puss a little while your Skilling. :]
